4     |   20   |  DTR (5vcc)             *below  |    n/c  |
8     |    5   |  CTS (low battery)      *below  | <-  5   |   7
2     |    3   |  RxD (no line voltage)  *below  | <-  3   |   2
5     |    7   |  Ground (Signal)                |     4   |  20
1     |    8   |  CD (on battery from UPS)       | <-  2   |   3
7     |    4   |  RTS (kill UPS power)           | ->  1   |   8
n/c   |    1   |  Frame/Case Gnd (optional)      |     9   |  22

