@cindex Cables
@cindex Windows

Due to inadequacies in the Win32 API, it is not possible to
set/clear/get all the serial port line
signals. apcupsd can detect: CTS, DSR, RNG,
and CD. It can set and clear: RTS and DTR.

This imposes a
few minor restrictions on the functionality of some of the cables. In
particular, LineDown on the Custom Simple cable, and Low Battery on
the 0023A cable are not implemented.

