UPSCABLE APC_940_0119A
    or APC_940_0127A
    or APC_940_0128A
    or APC_940_0020B
    or APC_940_0020C
@end example

here are typical signals you would expect to see in the output from
the various tests of apctest:

@example

Test 1 normal:              RTS for cables (0119A 0127A 0128A)
Test 2 no serial cable:     not important
Test 3 no AC power:         CTS for all cables
Test 4 batteries exhausted: CTS and CD for all cables
@end example

Note: @strong{RTS} if set in Test 1 will
probably also be set in all the other tests. This is not important,
what counts is the appearance of @strong{CTS}
when the power fails and additionally @strong{CD} when the batteries are low.

