Test 2 no serial cable:     not important
Test 3 no AC power:         RNG
Test 4 batteries exhausted: RNG and CD
@end example

Note: @strong{RTS} should never be set
in any of the tests as it is the killpower signal. What is important
is the appearance of @strong{RNG} when the
power fails and additionally @strong{CD} when
the batteries are low.

