an external hub connected to the root hub, and a mouse and
a serial converter connected to the external hub.

T:  Bus=00 Lev=00 Prnt=00 Port=00 Cnt=00 Dev#=  1 Spd=12  MxCh= 2
B:  Alloc= 28/900 us ( 3%), #Int=  2, #Iso=  0
